Specifically, the triangular-subdivision (trisub) and dual-construction
algorithms in `lib/topology/goldberg.ts` are TypeScript adaptations of
Anselm Levskaya's original CoffeeScript/JavaScript implementations in
`topo_operators.js`. The data structures have been rewritten to match
Paneler's PanelTopology format and the code has been ported to
TypeScript, but the underlying algorithmic approach is the same.

